人，然后就没生孩子，经常去各种医院查但也没发现问题。姐姐的婆婆就一直对姐姐不好，我爸爸妈妈想让她离婚，但是姐姐不想离，她说她很喜欢姐夫，舍不得。 就这样过了 5 年，然后我姐姐就认为是我姐夫的问题，想让他去检查一下，但是我姐姐婆婆却说生孩子是女人的事哪有她儿子的事等等等等，然后她们就吵了一架，姐姐就回来了，我不知道姐夫有没有帮姐姐说话，姐姐没跟我说，她就跟我说她想离婚，我不知道怎么办，就来问问"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "140 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/444784179"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I6rzirJ7HtYt6EAMaCDYxMTE5NTE4INi8r4EGMAw4zQFADHIJNDQ0Nzg0MTc5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1613779390.4444327", "card_id": "Q_444897340", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "海贼王两年后山治的实力已经从三大主力中退出了，会不会吃一颗恶魔果实加强他的实力，再重新回到三大主力？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-932820cbb20ec54bb2c37839ebe15d51_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "139 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/444897340"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I6rzirJ7HtYt6EAMaCDYxMTQ0NjMwIOzps4EGMAE4WkANcgk0NDQ4OTczNDB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1613779390.4447467", "card_id": "Q_426635230", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 195}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "电动牙刷是交智商税吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "为什么许多人都说用电动牙刷是交智商税呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-f83ceb7c131a74151129aa30c68f3e4e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "124 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/426635230"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I6rzirJ7HtYt6EAMaCDU3MDg3MTI0IMitvvwFMA048wZADnIJNDI2NjM1MjMweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1613779390.4450476", "card_id": "Q_55783301", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 5496}, "target": {"title_